{"tid":2282232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲蘋果我好鍾意，但有啲蘋果我好唔鍾意","createTime":"2020-11-11T16:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T02:02:05.000Z","uid":200663,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad09d29326e2d07b4b46db0205e3e1cc7c86841","tid":2282232,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:47:16.000Z","msg":"食得嘅蘋果我好鍾意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀得嘅蘋果我都好鍾意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係出 iPhone 嘅蘋果我就唔鍾意喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解？因為佢喺 TVB 落廣告啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>有網民投訴，最近Apple喺myTV SUPER投放密集式Ipad Air 4嘅廣告，小編去睇咗陣，的確差唔多每次廣告時間都見到ipad廣告。需知Apple親中就唔係今日嘅事，之前已經唔畀「黃App」上架，又唔畀員工戴黃口罩、用黑衫memoji，所以，大家罷得就罷喇！<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>🇨🇳 Apple助紂為虐歷史 🇨🇳</strong></span></p><br />\n⚠️ 於CCTVB投放密集式廣告<br />\n⚠️ 今年8月，Apple懷疑禁止員工佩戴黃色及印有「香港」字眼口罩，亦禁止員工使用黃衫或黑衫memoji，黃之鋒批評Apple對員工作政治審查<br />\n⚠️ 拒讓搜尋中資、親中企業的「共業REDSTOP」App上架<br />\n⚠️ 向《環時》跪低，以「危害執法人員和市民」為由將HKmap.Live從App Store下架<br />\n⚠️ 隱藏中華民國國旗emoji，並稱呼「台灣」為「中國台灣」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RphxcV0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRphxcV0.png&h=8058b2c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">派嬲，留言，懶打嘅可以拉落下面copy template，多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">😡 Apple Ipad Air 4 😡</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/apple/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fapple%2F&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=29e38f19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/apple/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y7vKOum.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7vKOum.png&h=7b01b60e&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n留言template: <br />\n<span class=\"small\"><em><span class=\"gold\">We, some of the Hong Kong customers, have noticed that your Hong Kong Branch is advertising in HK Television Broadcasts Limited (TVB), and are greatly disappointed by such acts.<br />\n-<br />\nTVB is a Pro-Chinese Communist Party(CCP) television station which reports biased and fake news, spreading propaganda for CCP, and trying its best to justify all misbehaviours that HK Government have done, including justifying the Chinese espionage in US, HK police brutality, the delay of LegCo election in 2020.<br />\n-<br />\nUS is a country that upholds universal values, for instance, pursuing freedom, democracy and human rights. We would like you to pressure your Hong Kong Branch to stop holding a candle to the devil and withdraw advertisements from TVB. Thank you, Apple, very much for understanding.<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/jCEjLuk.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCEjLuk.jpg&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=299dedac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/jCEjLuk.jpg</a></span></em></span>"},{"pid":"ec2c548f8fe594eba1844fa6b0bbffebcc02da84","tid":2282232,"uid":101507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:48:12.000Z","msg":"今鋪就撐陣狗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a985c58d1b5e9d9982dd68888230bdabc90a43","tid":2282232,"uid":204466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n--由ios版lihkg送出"},{"pid":"9bae399a78dc6c2f4d62fc1e97aa8e212ee9a524","tid":2282232,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05cb44c32229adc055dde2184169ff37c78b91bb","tid":2282232,"uid":192758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T17:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f66c901f51120c0899be6c634463d38ce0a1c9","tid":2282232,"uid":13067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:01:00.000Z","msg":"呢幾日出街見到好多後生用iphone12<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2060f0c707e5635b53203b63c95afa0f426eb078","tid":2282232,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}